page.title: 07POPULATION OF AREA. TREDIS
page.content: Treliddon,4,its cottages,8*. Minard,7,Rytha,2, Hendra,5. St.Winnoll's Cottages,4, Eglaroose,2. Triffle,10, Trewrickle,3.. The Bungalow,2, Tredrozzel,4*. Tregenna,6, Trewin,6*, Tredis House,6*, Higher Tredis,6.. Lower Tredis,4*, Tredis Cottages,4*. St. Winnolls,2, St.Winnolls Home,10*. Sconner,4*, Butter Villa,1. Berry,4, Trewall,7, Windrush,4*. Narkurs,50*(hamlet), Polbathic,94* (part of village),Tar Rose (Trerose!) Brake,40* (part of Bottlegate Estate, Downderry).. Figures marked * are approximate. Most of these people are farmers or farm-workers.There are some retired, and one swimming-pool builder, one actor, one television producer,two goat-keepers, one teacher of dancing..
